title: Days of Noah
cleaned_text: This is a MUST HEAR series for every Believer. The Church has GOT to wake up and be prepared for what is coming. Jesus said, "As it was in the days of Noah, so shall it be when the Son of Man returns." Listen to these audio clips to see how it was in the Days of Noah and what is happening in the world today concerning Transgenetics, cloning and the return of the Nephilim.
